Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:48.06,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How far we've come
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.60,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How much we've changed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:55.34,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A thousand nights and a million tears
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:10:02.94,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Now I can say that I've conquered my fear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:09.07,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If I could go back, what would I tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:12.97,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Wish you'd listen to the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:21.31,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Till then I'll be patiently waiting right here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.66,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Promises are kept deep in the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:04.85,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Bells are ringing so loud
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:09.66,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Our spirits will never die
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:17.99,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As long as there is something worth fighting for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.30,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We won't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:24.72,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if the stars falling down
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:29.19,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if the stars crash and burn the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:36.10,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We'll believe our voice will reach the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.38,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We won't give up till the end
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:44.98,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We won't give up till we smile again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.01,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Cuz we're alive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:53.65,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Cuz we made a promise to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.49,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.90,chaqu,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:48.06,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即便遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.60,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即便面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:55.34,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经过数千个黑夜 落下数万颗泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:10:02.94,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}此时我自信地说 我战胜了恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:09.07,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能回到过去 我该对你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:12.97,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了让你听到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:21.31,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我将永远在这里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.66,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们恪守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:04.85,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}警报高声响起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:09.66,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们的灵魂永生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:17.99,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要还有意义 我们便战斗不息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.30,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}永不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:24.72,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即便繁星陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:29.19,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}坠落在地 熊熊燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:36.10,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们的声音也定能响彻宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.38,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不到最后一刻 决不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:44.98,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不到重拾笑颜 决不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.01,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:53.65,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我们对世界许下了承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.49,chaqu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}许下了承诺
